### Create Listing (Listings Service)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/listings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Favorite Test Car",
  "make": "TestMake",
  "model": "TestModel",
  "year": 2024,
  "price": 50000000,
  "mileage": 1000,
  "condition": "Used",
