### Add to Favorites
POST http://localhost:8083/api/favorites/{{listing_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Check if Favorited
GET http://localhost:8083/api/favorites/check/{{listing_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Favorites
GET http://localhost:8083/api/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Favorites Count
GET http://localhost:8083/api/favorites/count
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Remove Favorite
DELETE http://localhost:8083/api/favorites/{{listing_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Clear All Favorites
DELETE http://localhost:8083/api/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
